<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/346971-can-i-read-the-ghost-road-as-a-stand-alone">Can I read The Ghost Road as a stand-alone story or am I really at a disadvantage not reading the first two? Also, if you had to choose to read only one book of the trilogy; which one do you think is the best stand-alone or would create the most discussion?

I intend to read all 3, but I want to propose this for a book club and I don&#39;t think thé entire trilogy would pass, but maybe one would.</a>
</div>
